----------------------------------------

This is the Kaltura Video assignment type with Moodle 2.

To install this plugin, copy the contents into
moodleroot/mod/assignment/type/kaltura, where moodleroot is the moodle 2
root (code) directory.

To use this resource you will also need the Kaltura Local Plugin, available
from: https://github.com/bwilkins/local-kaltura
